What: Remove the --disable-smp-locks configure option from master.<br>
<br>
Why: Use of this option produces incorrect results/undefined behavior<br>
when any shared memory BTL is in use. Since BTL usage is enabled even<br>
when using cm for point-to-point this option can never be safely used.<br>
